originalText.text: I love my lashes every time Jackie does them. She is always consistent. Putting full attention and detail into my lashes. She’s the first person that I’ve been to that has an array of lash types. I love long and natural no curl and she had it. I get compliments all the time. Plus my appointments are always on time. I don’t like waiting but I show the same respect by showing up on time. Her studio is clean and always cozy. Plus Jackie comes through with the blanket because I’m cold even when it’s not cold. Lol. I highly recommend!

originalText.text: Jackie is the absolute best!!! I’ve been coming here for over a year and she has a beautiful cozy lash studio right in her home, at a great location. Always clean, and she does an amazingly thorough and thoughtful job. Great price and I love chatting with her - HIGHLY recommend!!!!

originalText.text:
On 2/3/24 my daughter and I were searching for a new eyelash. WOW, EYELASH Bella new location was so clean and sterilized that one could literally eat off the floor.

Jackie the owner is perfection wrapped up all in one. During our consultation, she explained the difference between mink and cashmere lashes. Once I was able to feel the sample packages, cashmere won hands down. We also spoke about my eye shape and which eye design lashers would complement my facial structure.

Jackie is an excellent listener, she nailed everything we spoke about and oh yes, the cashmere lashes are soooooooooooooooooooooo light, you don’t even realize that you have extra lashes attached to your eyes.

In addition to the speechless service, I would be remised if I didn’t mention the CLEAN and soft blanket that she covers you in as you relax laying down with your eyes closed as she performs her magic.

My daughter and I were scheduled to revisit an old location, but after reading how their service had fallen, Eyelash Bella 5.0 rating was not disappointing.

Her prices are reasonable and affordable since the expectation timeline (if one maintains the lashes as instructed) the lashes will last around 2/3 weeks.

Eyelash Bella is my new eyelash location

originalText.text: I love Jackie and her work! I go to school in the UWS and so her location and the proximity is perfect for me. I can't see myself trusting someone else with my lashes again once I started going to Jackie. My eyes are super sensitive but Jackie manages to make me feel relaxed and comfortable. She is super nice and I can't wait to go back.
